是看到他們身上穿的說的 全都是土不拉機的。。。。。"},{"pid":"045feb2eaf00c4ed077298dddd262f0374a71d9e","tid":1663798,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:07:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d84b981bad4436f8920b334d004ff980e6c1fa7","tid":1663798,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:10:01.000Z","msg":"pushy"},{"pid":"d3bf200d33283602de50841cbdb47d088eebcf6a","tid":1663798,"uid":288648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67aKP1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67aKP1p.jpg&h=16302d28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHTXqzL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHTXqzL.jpg&h=76232431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVd4P1r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVd4P1r.jpg&h=296316ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57d2915ec6b9531e46259cf77b40eb87ff4690e6","tid":1663798,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:22:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2622355d9e5694337f16fae62db2e3b434c88bfe","tid":1663798,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T20:06:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc79bbdf55645b52f5e667fb9fea1a3b9d74299f","tid":1663798,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T20:14:56.000Z","msg":"[中後排有用POST!!] 做內街哨 check車係咪狗車！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663957</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a91ef46991ccd864ac2caf6a6dc6dfd9d52a641a","tid":1663798,"uid":51268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T00:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf121e5de649850a436c7d449c8716adc8327aa","tid":1663798,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dis